### Get all tickets
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ticket
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a passenger ticket
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 150,
  "trip_id": 1,
  "cashier_id": 2,
  "ticket_type": "passenger",
  "passenger_name": "John Doe",
  "discount": "student"
}

###

### Create a baggage ticket
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 80,
  "trip_id": 1,
  "cashier_id": 2,
  "ticket_type": "baggage",
  "sender_no": "09171234567",
  "dispatcher_no": "09187654321",
  "sender_name": "Jane Sender",
  "receiver_name": "Bob Receiver",
  "item": "1 box of clothes"
}

###

### Get ticket by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ticket/1
Accept: application/json

###

### PATCH ticket (note: edits trip, based on current handler)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/ticket/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "delayed"
}

###

### Delete ticket by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/ticket/1
Accept: application/json

### Get all baggage tickets
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ticket/baggage
Accept: application/json

###

### Get baggage ticket by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ticket/baggage/1
